     CSR         #SB920    BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD0         P2TOTL
     C                     Z-ADD0         P2SUMI
     C                     CALL 'AM#R02'
     C                     PARM           TISHID
     C                     PARM           TISHIT
     C                     PARM           TISURT
     C                     PARM           TINONY
     C                     PARM           TINKOJ
     C                     PARM           TINUKE
     C                     PARM           TIORD#
     C                     PARM           TIPALT
     C                     PARM           TIIAFB
     C                     PARM           TIIAFP
     C                     PARM           P2TOTL  30
     C                     PARM           P2SUMI  30
      *
     CSR         ESB920    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *  GET MANIFEST NUMBER FROM ORDER FILE.              *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #MANI     BEGSR
      *
      * default the order number from the 2D barcode as the manifest #
      * this is because for TMMC (and maybe others in the future) these
      * are one and the same.
      *
     C                     MOVELORNO      R1MAN#    P
      *
     C           K#19B     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           K@TOKU
     C                     KFLD           K@NONY
     C                     KFLD           K@NUKE
     C                     KFLD           K@INVN
     C                     KFLD           K@SKJY
      *
     C                     MOVELTINONY    K@NONY  40
     C                     MOVELTIDOCK    K@NUKE  4
     C                     MOVELORNO      K@INVN 16 P
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    K@SKJY  1
      *
     C           K#19B     SETLLAB#PL19B
     C           K#19B     READEAB#PL19B                 50
     C           *IN50     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           BAMHN     IFEQ PART
     C                     MOVELBAODRN    R1MAN#    P
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C           K#19B     READEAB#PL19B                 50
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     CSR         ESMANI    ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   verify container has not already been shorted.   *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB725    BEGSR
      *
     C           D2R       CHAINAM#PL01              90
     C           *IN90     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           R1SKJY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           R1SHME    ANDEQ'SHORT'
     C                     MOVEL'NG'      WKHNTE
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,11     MSG
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D2R       READEAM#PL01                  90
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     CSR                   ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      *   verify container has not already been packed.    *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #SB728    BEGSR
      *
     C           D2R       CHAINAM#PL01              90
     C           *IN90     DOWEQ*OFF
     C           R1SKJY    IFEQ *BLANK
     C           R1SHME    ANDEQ'OK'
     C                     MOVEL'NG'      WKHNTE
     C                     SETON                     3199
     C                     MOVELER,5      MSG
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C           D2R       READEAM#PL01                  90
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     CSR                   ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
**
INPUT PALLET TICKET.                                                         1
INPUT USER KANBAN.                                                           2
SCANNED ALL.                                                                 3
NO DATA.                                                                     4
ALREADY SCANNED.                                                             5
OTHER PALLET#.                                                               6
NO PALLET DATA.                                                              7
NO SHIPPING DATA.                                                            8
INPUT MANIFEST BARCODE.                                                      9
MANIFEST DOES NOT MATCH.                                                    10
ALREADY SHORTED.                                                            11
NAMC DOES NOT MATCH.                                                        12
SHIP DATE DOES NOT MATCH.                                                   13
SKID ID CANNOT BE BLANK.                                                    14
